Telkom South Africa Ltd. said it
reached an agreement through which an affiliate of Helios Towers
Nigeria Ltd. will acquire full ownership and control of Multi-
Links.  Multi-Links will be sold for about $10 million, and Telkom
with continue to provide interim operational funding to Multi-
Links while the transaction is completed, expected in August,
the South African company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
